=Bio=

"Autodidact and internationalist, experience in organic farming, social ecology, political economy and resettlement in rural areas of Iberian peninsula. After experience in Middle East and the contact with the Arab Spring and Kurdish Revolution, participated enthusiastically in new technologies of information and p2p social networks. In such a places the direct relation between networks and free access to information was the key point in the democratic revolution and initiation of cooperative economy.

Participant in alternative and social economy networks like Faircoin/Freedomcoop and CIC (Cooperativa Integral Catalana), after studying limitations of current projects and potentialities founded the Ecofintech Coop, a decentralized fintech cooperative platform following the principles of [[Distributed Cooperative Organization]] (DisCO) Governance Model.

Its current work is developing Confoederatio DTRADE platform, a decentralized trade and smart contracts blockchain and social infrastructure that got finalist in the EU award organized by LEDGER Project Fund."

